  "description": [
    "PENNEY COMPANY A NATIONWIDE INSTITUTION J C PENNEY COMPANY A NATIONWIDE INSTITUTION T C PENNEY COMPANY A NATIONWIDE INSTITUTION Putting Our House in Order To Meet New Conditions The J C PENNEY CO Operating 312 Department Stores in 27 States will on SATURDAY January 15th open its doors with Reconstruc tion Prices prevailing Every price in our stores is based upon our replacement price REGARDLESS OF PREVIOUS COST 3 M Z B BELIEVING the time has arrived when revision of prices is warranted by replacement value having discounted our merchandise thousands of dol lars in our inventory just completed we therefore give to the public the full benefit of the loss we sustain Remember we have said Our Replacement Price which should prove doub ly attractive Buying for 312 stores doing a yearly business of approximately Fifty Million Dollars should be sufficient proof that our replacement price is substantially lower than that of our competitors Do not confuse this with the usual markup and markdown special sale commonly helld by other merchants The J C Penney Company never has nor does it now believe in special sales Remember every article willl remain as priced until sold or forced by market"
  ],
